{
  "type": "AdaptiveCard",
  "$schema": "http://adaptivecards.io/schemas/adaptive-card.json",
  "version": "1.3",
  "body": [
    {
      "type": "TextBlock",
      "text": "Welcome to Fictitious, ",
      "wrap": true,
      "fontType": "Default",
      "size": "Medium",
      "weight": "Bolder"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextBlock",
      "text": "where we create uniquely romantic and sensual underwear just for you. I can help you do the following:",
      "wrap": true
    },
    {
      "type": "Container",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "ActionSet",
          "actions": [
              {
                "type": "Action.Submit",
                "title": "browse bestsellers",
                "data": "browse bestsellers"
              },
              {
                "type": "Action.Submit",
                "title": "check order status",
                "data": "check order status"
              },
              {
                "type": "Action.Submit",
                "title": "return a product",
                "data": "return a product"
              },
              {
                "type": "Action.Submit",
                "title": "get in touch",
                "data": "get in touch"
              }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "spacing": "Medium"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextBlock",
      "text": "I can also answer questions related to bra fitting and product care. Try asking things like \"How do I know if my bra is a perfect fit?\" or \"How often should I wash my bra?\". Type \"help\" any time to see the full list of requests I can handle.",
      "wrap": true,
      "spacing": "Medium"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextBlock",
      "text": "What can I do for you?",
      "wrap": true
    }
  ]
}